name: RARE G5 QQ Scarlet Chart Spock
bio: Uh, hi! I'm RARE G5 QQ Scarlet Chart Spock. I enjoy being a nevernude, eating until I loathe myself, and eating lasagna. When my owner isn't watching, I steal their snap-backs and use them for litter paper. I'm not sorry. I look forward to tricking babies with you.
